{"tid":1772750,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"陳茂波指人權法案損港人利益　不認同要「搵人搞自己」","createTime":"2019-12-07T02:27:07.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-07T05:30:25.000Z","uid":125168,"like":44,"dislike":83,"uniUserReply":123,"replies":[{"pid":"69a151a6601c05a9e805fc9ef37d5b349873eb22","tid":1772750,"uid":125168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-12-07T02:27:07.000Z","msg":"陳茂波指人權法案損港人利益　不認同要「搵人搞自己」<br />\n<br />\n財政司司長陳茂波表示，不會歡迎《香港人權與民主法案》獲通過，批評有關做法損害港人利益，亦損害國家尊嚴。陳茂波又指出，未知法案通過後會否對香港進口高新科技、工具產品帶來限制，影響發展成大灣區國際創科中心，亦令科研人員來港機會多了不確定性，但最終結果要視乎社會事件的發展。陳茂波出席一個電台節目時又表示，不認同香港自由出問題，亦不認同要「搵人搞自己」。他說由去年中美貿易糾紛開始，當局十分留意金融市場的風險，做了很多監控工夫，過去幾個月沒出現異常情況。<br />\n<br />\nRTHK 2019-12-07 10:20:31"},{"pid":"2b046b6464eff1d9057def154d581464ce10b024","tid":1772750,"uid":87780,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-07T02:27:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6ec87ecd053d5eaef20c4b068ab891fe16e1b063","tid":1772750,"uid":7043,"like":147,"dislike":0,"score":147,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-07T02:28:31.000Z","msg":"搞唔到我嫁喎<br />\n淨係搞到d損害港人民主既人嫁炸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6edee0e49fa24516020547d6cf19297cae251056","tid":1772750,"uid":103230,"like":75,"dislike":1,"score":74,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-12-07T02:28:37.000Z","msg":"冇人當你班狗奴才係自己人喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"46939bd8ba26794541f7594effeb1a5e22b000d5","tid":1772750,"uid":54564,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-07T02:28:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5661cdca831e2777286a2f145c453df42b94480e","tid":1772750,"uid":125168,"like":24,"dislike":0,"score":24,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-07T02:29:03.000Z","msg":"方向正確 繼續國際戰線令全球圍堵中共港共<img src=\"/assets/faces/nor